Let me tell you a little bit about us...
"Norm!!"
We are a friendly neighborhood sports bar where friends turn into family and you're treated as if you really are.
We have a fun and relaxed atmosphere where families and friends can come and watch the game, shoot some pool or partake in a friendly game of darts.  Poker and Bingo are just a few more activities that we offer throughout the week.
We provide incredible food and ice cold drinks with the lowest prices in the Cape, all with amazing service and a smile.
Smoking is permitted indoors and on our covered patio!
We've been at this exact location for over 25 years! Everyone is welcome! Come say hi, see what all the fuss is about and join our family today!
See you soon.
